{"tid":2001252,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"10年之關過不了 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-05-04T11:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T11:56:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b071a1bff2b66f9a7c0628ae82e3d0dd2134a94a","tid":2001252,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200503/20911165/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200503%2F20911165%2F&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1nvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=14781d60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200503%2F20911165%2F&h=add434a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200503/20911165/</a><br />\n<br />\n10年之關過不了 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200503/large/1588413329_d554.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200503%2Flarge%2F1588413329_d554.jpg&h=fb67ddc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有關中國大陸那愛國愛黨政治正確「10年保證」，不止影視界台前幕後「受惠」（或受制、受罪、受責、受苦、受難），其實各界都受到無形威脅，最好及早表忠，。。。。<br />\n時受罰甚至關閉──大陸簡（殘）體字中，「愛」沒有心，根本沒有愛，只有近似的畸胎「爱」，看來就是「受」。<br />\n<br />\n也許你們沒留意，幾個月來，有不少北上搵人仔的藝人因。。。。<br />\n至一線「明星」，已悄悄收拾細軟回流了。<br />\n<br />\n所謂「10年保證」，誰肯簽？別說藝人和各界精英了，連政棍奴才。。。。<br />\n跪拜的掌權者，能保證自己10年後不下台嗎？<br />\n<br />\n世上豈有海枯石爛矢志不渝的「高尚情操」？對於「忠」、「。。。。<br />\n最大考驗，而且考驗過不了關。<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB賤男黎某，妻子懷孕8個月臨盆在即，他也可無恥偷食鬧。。。。<br />\n原諒遊街做戲，企圖挽回跌至谷底的形象──據說他們讀書時期拍拖10年，也真脆弱。<br />\n<br />\n每對夫妻結婚誓詞，不管那款，都會承諾「從今天起，無論順境或。。。。<br />\n遠愛你、珍惜你，直到地老天荒&hellip;&hellip;」──「承諾」大家明白，但「永遠」是什麼？ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"c34df3f414e09b3e2914a778981b946dfb3dab41","tid":2001252,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:56:29.000Z","msg":"樓主唔想全cap，加多個字<br />\n「(... ...省略)  /  (節錄) 」<br />\n比就咁。。。。為好"}]}